			<div class="post-2469 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-uncategorized tag-bailout tag-jet-builders tag-obama">

				<div class="entry">

					<h2><a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/2012/05/31/obama-signs-billion-dollar-bailout-for-corp-jet-builders-patriotupdate-com/">Obama signs Billion-dollar Bailout For Corp. Jet builders [patriotupdate.com]</a></h2>

					<div class="post-info">
						<p>
							<span class="time">May 31, 2012</span>
															<span class="author">by <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/author/mktgeistmike/" title="Posts by mktgeistmike" rel="author">mktgeistmike</a></span>
																						<span class="post-comments"><a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/2012/05/31/obama-signs-billion-dollar-bailout-for-corp-jet-builders-patriotupdate-com/#respond" title="Comment on Obama signs Billion-dollar Bailout For Corp. Jet builders [patriotupdate.com]">Leave a comment</a></span>
																				</p>
					</div>

					<p>President Obama on Wednesday signed a reauthorization of <a href="http://www.washingtontimes.com/topics/the-export-import-bank/">the Export-Import Bank</a> that would raise its lending authority 40 percent to $140 billion by 2014 and pressed <a href="http://www.washingtontimes.com/topics/congress/">Congress</a> to pass a list of other top <a href="http://www.washingtontimes.com/topics/white-house/">White House</a> priorities aimed at creating jobs and boosting the economy.</p>
<p>Enough Republicans came to the 78-year-old bank’s aid to move the bill to the president’s desk earlier this month after conservatives in<a href="http://www.washingtontimes.com/topics/congress/">Congress</a> assailed it for meddling in the free market.</p>
<p><a href="http://patriotupdate.com/23747/obama-signs-billion-dollar-bailout-for-corp-jet-builders">Read more</a></p>
<div class="clear"></div>

				</div>

				<div class="post-meta">
					<p>
						<span class="categories">Filed under <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/category/uncategorized/" rel="category tag">Uncategorized</a></span>
