					<p>
						<span class="categories">Filed under <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/category/spain/" rel="category tag">Spain</a></span>
						<span class="tags">Tagged with <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/bailout/" rel="tag">Bailout</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/banks/" rel="tag">Banks</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/spanish/" rel="tag">Spanish</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/zerohedge/" rel="tag">Zerohedge</a></span>					</p>
